### Register User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Doe",
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "password123"
}

### Get Next Question (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/next
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check Answer (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/answer
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "answer": "Option1"
}

### Logout (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Subjects (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/subjects
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Topics (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/topics?subject=Indian Polity
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Filtered Questions (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/questions?subject=Indian Polity&topic=Fundamental Rights&difficulty=medium
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### v1: Get Questions (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/questions?subject=Indian Polity&topic=Fundamental Rights&difficulty=medium&count=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### v1: Submit Answer (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/questions/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "questionId": "test-question-id",
    "selectedOption": "Option2",
    "timeTaken": 25
}

### v1: User History (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/users/me/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Analytics Summary (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/analytics/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

