Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Submit Test (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/test/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "totalQuestions": 100,
    "correct": 85,
    "incorrect": 10,
    "unattempted": 5,
    "score": 85.0,
    "timeTaken": 3600,
    "subjectBreakdown": {
        "Indian Polity": {"total": 50, "correct": 45},
        "Geography": {"total": 50, "correct": 40}
    }
}

