GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/test/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Test Questions (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/test/questions?type=prelims&count=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Questions (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/search?query=climate change
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Bookmarks (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/bookmarks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add Bookmark (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/bookmarks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "questionId": "test-question-id",
    "note": "Important for revision"
}

### Delete Bookmark (Authenticated)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/bookmarks/test-bookmark-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Notes (Authenticated)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Note (Authenticated)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/notes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "UPSC Revision Notes",
    "content": "Key points on fundamental rights...",
    "subject": "Indian Polity"
}

### Update Note (Authenticated)
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/notes/test-note-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Title",
    "content": "Updated content..."
}

### Delete Note (Authenticated)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/notes/test-note-id
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

