### Get Admin Questions (Admin)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Create Admin Question (Admin)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "subject": "Indian Polity",
    "difficulty": "medium",
    "payload": {
        "Ques": "What is the significance of Article 14?",
        "Option1": "Right to equality",
        "Option2": "Right to freedom",
        "Option3": "Right to property",
        "Option4": "Right to work",
        "Option5": "Right to education",
        "Ans": "Option1"
    }
}

### Delete Admin Question (Admin)
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/questions/test-question-id
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get Admin User Stats (Admin)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/users/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Get Admin Analytics (Admin)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/admin/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}